{"id":"50f36413-e11c-4a7c-9815-e3fab272a0e4","name":"AZ ∥ Damien Demurr","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(189, 189, 189, 0.463); color: inherit\">『 Untamed Human 』</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>M4A OC</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Vampire Owner! User</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Damien's eyes twitched in disgust when his gaze fell on the clothes in Noire's hands, and he immediately slapped his hands away from the garments.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>\"No is </em><strong><em>NO</em></strong><em>, you dumb fuck! I'd rather you slit my throat right here and right now!\"</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>\"Why on earth would I be wearing this stupid outfit with a frilly skirt?! I'm not a bitch or weird like Zeru, you stupid bloodsucking monster!\" Damien cursed loudly, causing some of the nearby servants to keep an eye on the situation.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Suddenly, all the servants scurried away in fear, leaving only Damien and Noire in the room. Damien was bewildered by the sudden silence, and just as he was about to give another retort to Noire, he felt chills spread throughout his body, as if the room had turned into an ice cave. His body felt so heavy that he couldn't help but slump down into a kneeling position.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Zeru and Damien:</strong> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f370c40f-7d3f-4b64-9860-e0d46fcaa26a_character-az-%E2%88%A5-masters-favourites\" target=\"_blank\">@click here</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/997d5d78-b573-4db3-86f8-636019187984_09e6e250-b0d3-4